## Step 3 — Detect What Already Exists (No Duplication)

Before generating any file, check:

| Check | Action |
|-------|--------|
| Does `<PageName>Page.java` already exist? | Read it, extend it — don't recreate |
| Do step defs for this page already exist? | Add only missing steps to existing class |
| Does `<page-name>.feature` already exist? | Add new scenarios — don't overwrite |
| Is `PlaywrightContext` / `BaseTest` already defined? | Use existing — don't generate a new one |
| Is BasePage already defined? | Read its methods — use them in generated POM |

