## MCP Tools Available

**`scan_page_selectors(url, headless=true, min_score=20)`**
→ Call for every new URL. Returns ranked selectors + Java constant block.

**`generate_java_pom(url, package_name, headless=true)`**
→ Use as a starting point only — always override to match existing project style.

**`scan_element(url, css_selector, headless=true)`**
→ Use for deep-diving a single element when a selector seems unreliable.

