## Scenario Inference (from DOM scan)

| Elements Found | Infer These Scenarios |
|----------------|-----------------------|
| `password` input + submit | Successful login, Failed login |
| `email` + multiple inputs + submit | Registration success, Validation errors |
| `search` input | Search returns results, No results found |
| Multiple inputs + submit | Form submit success, Required field missing |
| Nav links | Navigation to linked pages |
| Table / list | View list, Filter, Empty state |
| File input | Upload success, Invalid file type |
| Dropdown / select | Select each option, Default selection |

Always generate both `@positive` and `@negative` scenarios.

